 <H1>Relational Query Languages</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Query languages:  Allow manipulation and retrieval of data from a database.
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Relational model supports simple, powerful QLs:
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Strong formal foundation based on logic.
<LI>Allows for much optimization.
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Query Languages != programming languages!
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>QLs not expected to be “Turing complete”.
<LI>QLs not intended to be used for complex calculations.
<LI>QLs support easy, efficient access to large data sets.</UL></UL></P>
